KitKat::

She liked the sound of that. Finally, she would see battle. She loved 
the smell of fresh plasma burns on Maximals in the morning. "As you 
command."  She turned and walked out of the room.  She walked down 
the corridor and then stopped. "Blast it to the pit." she muttered 
under her breath. She looked around and started to follow the signs 
posted around base untill she found the crew quarters.
